message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
Finally, I've been waiting ages to speak to someone. My claim hasn't been processed yet, and I submitted it weeks ago!
I'm deeply sorry to hear about the delay in processing your claim. To better assist you, before proceeding, can you confirm your full name, date of birth, first line of address, and postcode, please?
Ugh, fine. It's Sarah Johnson, 05/12/1990, 123 Park Street, AB1 2CD.
Thank you for completing security, Sarah. I'll look into your claim now.
Great, can you hurry it up? I really need this sorted out as soon as possible.
I completely understand the urgency, Sarah. It seems there has been a delay in processing. A possible resolution could be to escalate your claim for immediate review. Would that work for you?
Yes, that's what I want. Please do it quickly.
Thank you for your patience, Sarah. I've escalated your claim for immediate review. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Just get this sorted, please.
I'm glad that I was able to help. If you have any more concerns, feel free to reach out. Have a great day, Sarah!
